title: Asian American Resource and Cultural Center | University of Illinois at Chicago
text: The Asian American Resource and Cultural Center supports the needs of Asian Americans at UIC and offers social, cultural, and educational programs to those interested in expanding their knowledge about Asian Americans.
Please email AARCC@uic.edu or call 312-413-9569 and someone will respond during business hours.
All upcoming AARCC Lunchbox programs and community programs have been cancelled until further notice.
Please visit this page and our Facebook Page for any updates.
For the latest news and information about COVID-19 to the campus community, visit https://today.uic.edu/coronavirus.
